response.overview: Released from a mental health facility after recovering from a tragic accident, Tulip Lenoux lives in a purgatorial state between the natural world and dream world. Bound to her dead lover through a suicide pact gone wrong, Tulipâ€™s semi-lucid daily wanderings and mind-bending fever dreams are clouded by trauma, obsession, heartbreak, and unanswered questions regarding the missing body of her lost love. Meanwhile, dark forces are at work when Tulip unwittingly stumbles into the cult-like world of the Roma Key Club and its henchmen, with concurrent storylines of necromancy, supernatural procreation, personal limbo, and practical magic.
response.title: Tethered To The Ether
